<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.3.8">
<l>nāḷu niṉṟaṭu namapaḻa maiyaṅkoṭu viṉaiyuṭaṉē</l>
<l>māḷumōr kuṟaivillai maṉaṉaka malamaṟak kaḻuvi</l>
<l>nāḷunan tiruvuṭai yaṭikaṭan nalaṅkaḻal vaṇaṅki</l>
<l>māḷumō riṭattilum vaṇakkoṭu māḷvatu valamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Standing daily our deadly ancient cruel deeds will die all together.</l>
<l>There will be not one lack. Cleansing fully enough the inside of [our] mind,</l>
<l>daily bowing to the good ankletted [feet] of the lord who possesses Śrī,</l>
<l>even one time when dying with obeissance dying will be gain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
